	   <tr><td colspan=2>as you wish  =)<br><br>(this asumes you have no missed notes) ok what i do is hotkey 4-6 songs (always have selos and healing hotkeyed). then hit 1 to start the song in the first hotkey box. wait bout 2 secs (you'll learn the timing eventually) stop it, then start another. you should still get your mssg of the first songs effect even though you started another song, thats if your good.<br><br>otherwise start a song and hit f9 (view) a couple times to see yourself from a distance, RIGHT when you see any kind of effect that you know from the bard song (i look for the tanish dots from haste songs) stop the song and start number 2. so it'll look like this:<br><br>1<br>pause 2 secs<br>2<br>pause 2 secs<br>3<br>pause 2 secs<br>4<br>rinse and repeat<br><br>you might be able to twist 5 songs if your connection is good (cable or DSL). good luck!<br><br>Taamas Starsinger<br>34th Season<br>House of Wargoth<br>Saryrn<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
